{
  "stem": "13524.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] You know, there are these scenes that come to me, when I think of Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I also very often used to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because I was too tired, not enough food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Waiting for my mother to come home, to see what she brought from that work place, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's where she worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] .",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a place where they were collecting produce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not that Mother had access to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They only used to go to clean, to clean the place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Occasionally she would meet somebody in the street, and they would give her a bit of food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that didn't last terribly long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have cut off the going out to work constantly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The working places were taken by the Poles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mother became redundant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she looked for other places.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she ended up again in that potato-peeling place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that was also-- the purpose was to get some potatoes, to get something to eat, to bring some to my father and to me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Mother made sure that she eats down there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they were allowed, really, to cook a little bit of potatoes at lunchtime and eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were not allowed to eat raw potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they would eat the stock up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, my mother, and myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister was with us in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not tell you that my sister-- when we have, when the parents have heard that ghetto is being liquidated, she has found somebody who wanted to take her as wife, over the border, to help her to escape to another country.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She went via Bochnia, it's a place in Galicia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And down there they have met somebody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And naturally they bribed him well.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
